data.description: Potential to assume an FHA mortgage at 2.25%. Inquire for more details. Spacious, bright an airy home located in absolutely lovely neighborhood on a low-traffic street. 4 expansively sized bedrooms as well as a beautiful office, 3 bathrooms, 3 car garage, fully fenced backyard. Safe room is made concrete walls and created to protect during severe weather, a great feature in any Kansas home. Tall kitchen cabinets, granite counters, tile backsplash, and gas range. Wonderful school district, close to shopping, easy access to both I-70 and K-10.
